author: The Current
description:
Watch and listen to Laufey's solo acoustic performance of "From The Start"
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Icelandic artist Laufey released her third album, "A Matter of Time," on August 22, 2025. Back in 2023, Laufey visited The Current to perform a couple of solo renditions of songs from her second album, "Bewitched." Watch Laufey's performance of "From The Start," above. 

All of Laufey's albums, 2022's "Everything I Know About Love," 2023's "Bewitched" and 2025's "A Matter of Time," are available on @AWAL.

Musician
Laufey – guitar and vocals

Credits
Guest – @laufey 
Producer – Derrick Stevens
Video Director – Josh Sauvageau
Camera Operators – Josh Sauvageau, Micah Kopecky
Audio – Eric Xu Romani
Graphics – Natalia Toledo
Digital Producer – Luke Taylor
